        "container_padding_bottom": 40,
        "container_padding_left": 20,
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/9bbe9121-18f7-4785-aba3-08dc51b30e1f.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_width": 45,
        "image_radius": 8,
        "heading": "Power Your Outdoors with Mowtivated Power Equipment!",
        "heading_color": "#000000",
        "heading_font_size": 40,
        "text": "Mowtivated Power Equipment is your trusted destination for high-quality outdoor equipment and reliable service. As a locally driven business, we’re committed to helping homeowners and professionals get the job done right with equipment they can depend on.\n\nWe offer a wide range of top-performing brands, along with expert repair and maintenance services for most makes and models. Whether you're upgrading your gear or keeping your current equipment in peak condition, our team is here to support you every step of the way.\n\nAt Mowtivated Power Equipment, we know that performance and durability matter. That’s why we provide only dependable products designed to handle tough outdoor tasks with ease. From lawn mowers and trimmers to chainsaws, blowers, and seasonal equipment — we’ve got everything you need to stay productive year-round.",
        "text_color": "#333333",
        "text_font_size": 18,
        "text_align": "left",
        "button_label": "Contact Us Now",
        "button_link": "shopify://pages/contact",
        "button_new_tab": false,
        "button_color": "#c4100c",
        "button_text_color": "#ffffff",
